ads\/2013\/08\/Schermata-2013-08-16-alle-16.13.22.png?resize=125%2C117&amp;ssl=1 125w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/insidecode.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/Schermata-2013-08-16-alle-16.13.22.png?resize=220%2C207&amp;ssl=1 220w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/insidecode.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/Schermata-2013-08-16-alle-16.13.22.png?w=722&amp;ssl=1 722w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2>WORA &#8211; multipiattaforma<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<p>Il gioco \u00e8 stato progettato usando la libreria &#8220;PlayN&#8221; di Google, pertanto il progetto \u00e8 completamente <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>WORA<\/strong><\/span> (write once, run everywhere), ovvero pu\u00f2 essere eseguito sulle maggiori piattaforme (Pc, Mac, Linux, Android, iOS, Html5) senza modificare una riga di codice.<\/p>\n<p>BomberMan eseguito sulla piattaforma di sviluppo <strong>Olinuxino<\/strong> (Android e linux):<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/insidecode.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/WP_20130802_006.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"517\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/insidecode.it\/sapienza-games-saga-bomberman-on-the-go\/wp_20130802_006\/\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/insidecode.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/WP_20130802_006.jpg?fit=2592%2C1456&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2592,1456\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.4&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Lumia 620&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1375465984&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;500&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.050015&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"WP_20130802_006\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/insidecode.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/WP_20130802_006.jpg?fit=250%2C140&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\